welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Arbatache, Algeria! Get ready to experience the charm of our city, known for its rich history and stunning landscapes. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Arbatache has to offer."

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Houari Boumediene Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal primarily used for domestic flights within Algeria.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A newly constructed terminal dedicated to international flights, providing modern facilities and services.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may have limited coverage in certain areas.
